Here is the revised **Privacy Policy** tailored for **Kokeb Mobile Banking**:

---

# Privacy Policy

### Introduction

Our Privacy Policy helps you understand what information we collect at **Kokeb Mobile Banking**, how we use it, and what choices you have.

**Kokeb Mobile Banking** is developed and provided by **Kokeb** as a free app. This SERVICE is offered at no cost and is intended for use as is.

By using our Service, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy. The personal information we collect is used to provide and improve the Service. We will not use or share your information with anyone except as described in this Privacy Policy.

The terms used in this Privacy Policy have the same meanings as in our Terms and Conditions, unless otherwise defined.

---

### Information Collection and Use

To deliver a better user experience, we may require you to provide certain personally identifiable information, including but not limited to:

* Full name
* Phone number
* Email address
* Gender
* Location
* Profile picture
* Bank account details (e.g., account number)

This information will be retained and used as outlined in this Privacy Policy. We may also use third-party services that collect information to identify you for the purpose of providing essential banking services and ensuring security.

---

### Cookies

Cookies are small data files used to identify your device anonymously. They are sent to your browser from websites you visit and may be stored in your device’s memory.

Kokeb Mobile Banking does **not** use cookies directly. However, third-party libraries or services integrated into the app may use cookies to improve service quality. You can choose to accept or refuse these cookies. Refusing cookies may affect some app functionalities.

---

### Location Information

Some features of the app may require access to your device’s location. Location data is used only for the purpose of enabling specific services such as branch or ATM locator functionalities and is not shared beyond that scope.

---

### Device Information

We may collect device-specific information (such as model, OS version, and unique identifiers) for analytics, fraud prevention, and security purposes. This data does not include information that personally identifies the user.

---

### Service Providers

We may engage third-party companies and individuals for the following reasons:

* To facilitate our Service
* To perform Service-related operations on our behalf
* To assist in analyzing app usage
* To provide customer support or technical services

These third parties may access your Personal Information only to perform the tasks assigned to them and are obligated not to disclose or use it for any other purpose.

---

### Security

We value your trust in sharing your Personal Information. Therefore, we implement commercially reasonable security measures to protect it. However, no method of transmission over the Internet or method of electronic storage is 100% secure. While we strive to protect your data, we cannot guarantee absolute security.

---

### Children’s Privacy

Our Service is not intended for children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from anyone under 13. If we become aware that a child under 13 has provided us with personal data, we will take steps to delete it immediately. If you are a parent or guardian and discover your child has shared personal information with us, please contact us.

---

### Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We advise you to review this page periodically for any updates. Changes are effective immediately after they are posted on this page.

---

### Contact Us

If you have any questions or suggestions about our Privacy Policy, please contact us:

**Email:** [support@kokebbank.com](mailto:support@kokebbank.com) (replace with your actual email if needed)

